subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Despite being seeded seventh in the N.C.A.A. tournament, the Scarlet Knights (21-12) have made the Round of 16 for the fifth season in a row.
